Allegations of voter intimidation and bribery marred the Dabaso Ward by-election in Kilifi County on Tuesday.
There was also choas at the Dabaso Primary School polling centre, which forced security personnel to disperse crowds.
The Dabaso MCA seat fell vacant after the High Court nullified the August 7, 2017 election of Emmanuel Changawa of the Orange Democratic Movement (ODM).



